QuestData.Title: Dreadlords!
QuestData.Description:
This is the fifth dreadlord I have found infiltrating our forces this week. Unchecked they can cause tremendous damage to our foothold here.
In life I learned how to identify these creatures from a demon hunter. It makes it far easier for me to locate them, but I cannot be in all places at once.
We must report these findings to the Primus.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with the Primus in Korthia.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with the Primus in Korthia.
